original_title: Princess Diana, Freddie and Kenny: ‘One Normal Night’
overview: This short film takes place on the night that Freddie Mercury and Kenny Everett put a disguise on their good friend, Princess Diana, and took her out for a night on the town, ending up at the Vauxhall Tavern and encountering a drag queen named Gareth.
title: Princess Diana, Freddie and Kenny: ‘One Normal Night’
